{% section "Agent First Impressions" %}
<!-- What did agents conclude at this phase? Copy key FIRST_IMPRESSION blocks here. -->
<!-- Source: scripts/audit_results/ or vault Agent-Outbox/ -->

```dataview
TABLE WITHOUT ID
  file.link AS "Finding",
  confidence_level AS "Conf",
  hypothesis_support AS "H",
  source_quality AS "Quality"
FROM "00-SHARED/Agent-Outbox"
WHERE pipeline_run = this.run_id
SORT confidence_level DESC
LIMIT 10
```
{% endsection %}

