{% section "Gate Decision" %}
<!-- Your decision: pass, block, or request more analysis. -->

- [ ] **PASS** — proceed to next phase (`python3 scripts/gate_pass.py pass {{ gate_num }}`)
- [ ] **BLOCK** — stop pipeline, needs investigation (`python3 scripts/gate_pass.py block {{ gate_num }}`)
- [ ] **RED-TEAM** — request adversarial analysis on specific hypothesis

